                <![CDATA[<p>东风风行香港总代理东腾车业正式发布全新右軚版本纯电 SUV「Forthing Friday」（风行 05）登陆香港，标志该品牌加速迈向全面电动化之路的重要一步。新车融合年轻化设计与前沿智能科技，并以港币 HK$218,000 的一换一意向价进军本地市场，冀能吸引寻求实用与个性兼备的电动车买家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>东风柳汽旗下的「风行」品牌近年积极推动新能源转型，风行 05 为品牌「光合未来」计划的首个重要成果。官方表示，品牌正计划于未来 3 年全面电动化、5 年内全面停产燃油车，并期望 2030 年实现碳达峰、2060 年达至碳中和。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>风行 05 外形设计以「旷野电动驰骋」为主题，车头采用封闭式进气格栅及蜂窝装饰面板，搭配分体式 LED 头灯，营造出强烈科技感。车尾配备贯穿式天际线 LED 尾灯，视觉效果鲜明突出。车身尺寸为 4600mm × 1860mm × 1680mm，轴距达 2715mm，结合短悬长轴设计，空间感与灵活度兼具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>动力方面，前轮驱动的风行 05 搭载由 BYD 弗迪动力提供的 150kW 永磁同步电机，最大马力 201 匹，峰值扭力达 340Nm，0 至 100km/h 加速需时 7.9 秒。配合 64.4kWh 铠甲电池提供高达 500 公里 CLTC 续航力，并支援 35 分钟由 0% 快充至 80%，应付城市及长途驾驶均游刃有余。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车箱配置方面，风行 05 采用对称式中控台配搭圆形出风口，塑造年轻与现代感氛围。主驾座位设有电动按摩座椅连冷凳功能、双联屏智慧座舱、同时支援 Apple CarPlay 及 Android Auto。随车配备 480 公升尾箱与多个收纳位，对家庭出行需求提供全面支援。新车配备 FX-Drive 智能驾驶系统，支援 L2+ 级辅助驾驶功能，包括前方碰撞预警、车道保持、360 度全景影像及智能限速提醒等共 12 项主动安全功能，加上泊车雷达与 ABS、EBS 制动系统，为用户提供更全面驾驶保障。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>规格表:</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1299681 alignleft" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/05.png" alt="" width="675" height="410" /></p><br /><b>
